<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Zawlnei genlawk van Mang Vawnchawih.
 David suona hung pieng ding;
 Lengmang Kaisar Lal gam kimvel ah a than laii'n,
 Angel lopi hung tuol kum in, A hun phawng ui Belampute;
 &quot;Ngaiun tuni'n David khawpi achun,
 Hukdampa a pieng tai, A min Lal Krista chuh,
 Na het nang un Nausen puontuom Gankuong sung achun mu'n lau.&quot;

[V2]
 A min mak chamna Van Lalmang,
 Lengmang Pathien hat chungnung;
 Kumsawtpa Lalmang hung hin tin,
 A gamin tuoi ni nei puona,
 Kumsawt tawplo Lalmang hung hina, Amen.

[V3]
 2. Tichun Van mi thiengtho simsen
 Loh ten kipakna la san;
 Bawng-In tawma Nausen mimbang pieng a chawian ui,
 Singkhuola zing-zin michingte, Leh van aksi vak hawihtak chun;
 A hun zuon ui van Lal vawnchawih Nausen,
 Mimbang a a pien na, Bethlehem a Bawng-In
 Belamputen le kipak in; Lal chibai a va buk ui.

[V4]
 3. Sietlei hingmi namtin vawnchawih,
 Thihna dailim a leng te;
 Van Lal pienna lawm din Bethlehem ah chieh hitiu,
 Zie gam thiengtho a Nausen chuh, A min 'Mak' 'Lalmang' chu ahii,
 I neih go thil phate chawiin kipah
 Na zaila sakawm in, Chibai vabuk hitiu,
 Hallelujah lopi pen hen, Kumsawt Lengmang hung pieng chuh!</lyrics>
<title>Chamna Van Lalmang</title>
<author>Sawngkhawkhai</author>
<hymn_number>36</hymn_number>
</song>